This directory contains additions to certain applications for providing
DNSSEC validation.

[1]
The libspf2-1.0.4_dnssec_patch.txt file contains a patch to libspf2-1.0.4
that provides DNSSEC validation.

libspf2 can be downloaded from http://www.libspf2.org/download.html

To apply this patch, download libspf2-1.0.4.tar.gz from the above website.
Unzip and untar it by:

	tar -xvzf libspf2-1.0.4.tar.gz

Go to the libspf2-1.0.4 directory:

	cd libspf2-1.0.4

Now apply the above patch by:

	patch -p 0 -b -z .orig </path/to/patch/libspf2-1.0.4_dnssec_patch.txt

This will apply the patch and store the original files with a .orig suffix.

Configure, compile and install libspf2 as per the instructions given in the
libspf2-1.0.4 distribution.

[2]
The 'sendmail' directory contains milters for sendmail that perform DNSSEC
validation for the sendmail Mail Transfer Agent.
